# GeoScope uses one of two vision providers. Configure ONE of these:

# Option A — Gemini (FREE, no credit card required)
# Get a key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# Free tier: 1,500 requests/day on gemini-2.5-flash
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Option B — Claude (paid, ~$0.003 per image, higher quality)
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com → API Keys
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# If both are set, Gemini takes priority.
